	<Name>Final Fight Guy (USA)</Name>
	<plot>Final Fight Guy is a side scrolling fighter game in the likes Double Dragon. You can choose between Guy and Haggar. Guy and Haggar are determined to rid Metro City of  MAD GEAR, the local street gang. You can also pick up and use various melee weapons that gang members tend to drop when you hit them. The game also has some bonus levels in which you can score extra lifes.Cheat: Bonus creditsIf the player initials entered for the top 3 high scores are CAP, COM, GUY and in that order, you will begin a new game with 5 credits instead of 3.</plot>
